\uc0\u9473 \u9473 \u9473  THE PRODUCT \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \
MIZAN Health (\uc0\u1605 \u1610 \u1586 \u1575 \u1606  = "balance" in Arabic) is a \
two-interface AI-powered obesity care platform.\
\
PRIMARY MARKET: KSA and UAE physician offices/clinics\
SECONDARY MARKET: US obesity medicine practices with \
  diverse patient panels (Arab-American, South Asian, \
  Middle Eastern)\
\
TWO INTERFACES:\
1. CLINIC DASHBOARD \'97 physician/staff web app\
   Manages patients, views weekly digests, monitors trends,\
   tracks engagement and meal scores\
\
2. PATIENT APP \'97 mobile-first PWA\
   Daily food photo logging with AI analysis, weight \
   tracking, water intake, contextual logging, streaks\
\
POSITIONING: \
"The only obesity management platform built for Gulf-region \
clinical practice \'97 culturally specific, AI-powered, \
physician-supervised."\
\
NOT a consumer calorie app. NOT competing with Cal AI \
or MyFitnessPal directly. This is B2B clinical tool sold \
to physician offices, with the patient app as the \
engagement layer.\
\
KEY DIFFERENTIATORS:\
1. Gulf cultural specificity (Arabic, Gulf dishes, Ramadan \
   mode) \'97 no competitor has this\
2. Physician-supervised model \'97 patients enrolled BY their \
   doctor, not self-enrolled\
3. Clinical data owned by clinic not patient\
4. PharmD license (founder) + physician brother = \
   pharmacy capability (future)\
5. First mover in KSA/UAE clinical obesity tech\
6. Confirm-before-save food logging (prevents AI errors)\
7. Bilingual EN/AR throughout\
