\uc0\u9473 \u9473 \u9473  AI MODELS \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \
Food photo analysis: claude-sonnet-4-6\
  - Vision AI, analyzes food photos\
  - Returns: dish_name, tag, note_en, note_ar,\
    calories_estimate_low/high, meal_type,\
    protein_g, carbs_g, fat_g\
  - User input wrapped in XML to prevent injection:\
    <patient_input>\{foodNameHint\}</patient_input>\
  - Rate limited: 10 analyses per patient per day\
\
Daily tip: claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\
  - 20x cheaper than Sonnet\
  - Cached in daily_tips table (one per patient per day)\
  - Bilingual EN/AR output\
\
Food logging flow (TWO-STEP, confirmed Mar 2026):\
  1. POST /api/food-log/analyze \'97 calls Claude, \
     returns result JSON, does NOT save to DB\
  2. User sees pending card: "Does this look right?"\
  3. POST /api/food-log/confirm \'97 saves to DB,\
     computes meal_score server-side, returns score\
  This prevents AI misidentification errors (e.g.,\
  kabsa identified as chocolate donut in testing)\
\
Meal score computation (server-side at confirm):\
  green tag \uc0\u8594  8-9 (randomized)\
  yellow tag \uc0\u8594  5-7 (randomized)\
  red tag \uc0\u8594  2-4 (randomized)\
